    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road? I\u2019m parting ways with my car, and it\u2019s been such a fantastic companion. It\u2019s in solid shape, runs super smoothly, and has been well-loved throughout its time with me. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways! I\u2019d love for it to go to a great new home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by and take it for a spin. Can't wait to hear from you!",
