    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Combining mechanical excellence with a distinguished aesthetic, it has been curated to ensure peak performance and consistent reliability. Offering a sophisticated driving experience and a comprehensive service history, this selection provides exceptional value for those who demand both quality and substance in their next acquisition.",
      "price": 34800.0,
